    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine Domini. Anno ab incarnacione Domini millesimo centesimo vigesimo
                        tercio, die nono mensis novembris, indictione secunda, <placeName
                            ref="#places/594">Ravenne</placeName>. Peto a te in Dei nomine <persName
                            key="#Abbots" ref="#people/4308">Aurelio</persName>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abbate</rs>
                        <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterio</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Curtes #Landed_possessions #Cereals #Maiores #Minores #Wine #Fruits/vegetables #Linen #Pigs #Poultry #Rent_in_kind #Rent_in_money #Operae #Missus #Levies #Monasteries"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/1460">Sancte Marie in <placeName
                                ref="#places/4179">Pomposia</placeName></orgName>, cum consensu
                        monachorum eiusdem monasterii, uti michi in Christi nomine <persName
                            key="#Coloni/tenants"><name ref="Petrus">Petro</name></persName> de
                                <persName><name ref="Petrus de Vitalis">Petro de
                            Vitali</name></persName> seu filiis meis masculis, secundum quod legitur
                        in <rs key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis">libello</rs> patris mei − et si
                        sine filiis ut supra legitur obiero, cadat dicenda res in <persName><name
                                ref="Dominicus">Dominico</name></persName> fratre meo sub dominio
                        matris mee donec vixerit − per libellum concedis michi, idest quantum habeo
                        et detineo per anticum libellum in <rs key="#Curtes">curte</rs> vestra que
                        vocatur <geogName
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Curtes #Landed_possessions #Cereals #Maiores #Minores #Wine #Fruits/vegetables #Linen #Pigs #Poultry #Rent_in_kind #Rent_in_money #Operae #Missus #Levies"
                            ref="#estates/2425"><placeName
                                key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Curtes #Landed_possessions #Cereals #Maiores #Minores #Wine #Fruits/vegetables #Linen #Pigs #Poultry #Rent_in_kind #Rent_in_money #Operae #Missus #Levies"
                                ref="#places/1574">Prata</placeName></geogName>, cum <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">terris</rs>, <rs key="#Wine">vineis</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Cereals">campis</rs>, arbustis, <rs key="#Fruits/vegetables"
                            >arboribus</rs> atque cum omnibus sibi pertinentibus, constitutum <rs
                            key="#Plebs">plebe</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Curtes #Landed_possessions #Cereals #Maiores #Minores #Wine #Fruits/vegetables #Linen #Pigs #Poultry #Rent_in_kind #Rent_in_money #Operae #Missus #Levies #Plebs"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/1490">Sancti Iohannis in Assiata</orgName>; et
                        conceditis mihi <rs key="#Size">decem tornaturias</rs>
                        <rs key="#Landed_possessions">terre</rs> ad perticam ipsius loci pro illa
                        quam habet <persName key="#Landed_possessions #Size"><name ref="Menzolinus"
                                >Menzollinus</name></persName> de meo libello. Habendum, tenendum,
                        cultandum, laborandum et in omnibus meliorandum in annis advenientibus
                        viginti et novem ad renovandum. Et <rs key="#Levies">terraticum</rs> vobis
                        vestrisque successoribus dare debeatis de omni <rs key="#Cereals #Maiores"
                            >labore maiore</rs> modium quintum, <rs key="#Cereals #Minores"
                            >minutum</rs> sextum, <rs key="#Linen">lino</rs> mannam sextam, <rs
                            key="#Wine">vino</rs> anforam terciam, arbore pecto ponente semel; et
                        dare debeamus fogaciam unam et <rs key="#Poultry">pullos</rs> duos in Sancto
                        Apollinari et in Natale <rs key="#Pigs">spallam</rs> unam et <rs
                            key="#Rent_in_money">solidos tres denariorum Veneticorum</rs>; et unum
                        hominem vobis dabo ad vestrum servicium semel in anno ad Pomposea et <rs
                            key="#Operae">operam</rs> vobis facere debeamus secundum anticum
                        libellum et si libellus non aparuerit illas operas vobis faciemus ut antiqui
                        homines ipsius loci testabunt pater meus fecisse per anticum libellum. Et
                        non licead nobis triturare neque vindemiare sine iussione vestra; vos et
                        vestrum <rs key="#Missus">missum</rs> cum onore et obediencia susipere
                        debeamus; adductum terraticum et redditum usque in hac civitate Ravenne, in
                        claustro <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/1480">Sancti Stefani
                            maioris</orgName> per nos <rs key="#Coloni/tenants">colonos</rs>. Pro eo
                        quia do vobis, calciarii nomine, denariorum Lucensium inforciatorum solidos
                        decem et septem. Si quis vero partis nostre contra hanc peticionem ire
                        tentaverit, det pars parti fidem servanti, nomine pene, <rs key="#Penalty"
                            >auri uncias duas</rs> et soluta pena maneat firma ec peticio libelli.
                        Ego <persName key="#Tabellio"><name ref="Hugo">Ugo</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Tabellio">tabellio</rs> Ravennas scripsi hanc paginam ut supra
                        legitur.</ab>
                </div>
